WEBVTT

00:07:57.320 --> 00:08:00.256
they grow herbs in healthy soil,

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:03.216
free of chemicals,
pesticides, fertilizers,

00:08:03.240 --> 00:08:05.576
genetically modified products --

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:07.120
healthy food.

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:09.536
And when their product is sold

00:08:09.560 --> 00:08:12.416
all over the city of Detroit
in local markets,

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:15.120
they get a hundred percent
of the proceeds from the sale.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:18.480
In a city like Detroit,

00:08:19.320 --> 00:08:24.776
where far too many, far too many
African Americans are dying

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:27.480
as a result of diet-related diseases,

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:31.416
restaurants, they have a huge role to play